<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.9.1">
<l>tāyē tantaiyeṉṟun tāramēkiḷai makkaḷeṉṟum</l>
<l>nōyē paṭṭoḻintē ṉuṉṉaikkāṇpatō rācaiyiṉāl,</l>
<l>vēyēy pūmpoḻilcūḻ viraiyārtiru vēṅkaṭavā</l>
<l>nāyēṉ vantaṭaintēṉ nalkiyāḷeṉṉaik koṇṭaruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You of fragrance-filled Tiruvēṅkaṭam encircled by blooming gardens</l>
<l rend="indent">next to bamboo [thickets],</l>
<l>Having suffered the disease [of life] calling, “mother [and] father,”</l>
<l rend="indent">and calling, “wife, kin, [and] kids,”</l>
<l>I, who left [them], because of the one desire of seeing you,</l>
<l>I, a dog, came [here and] took refuge; be gracious, kindly receiving me,</l>
<l rend="indent">your servant, in service.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
